<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/fonts.css">
  <title><%= title || "Camverse" %></title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800" style="font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif;">
  <%- include('partials/userNavbar', { navbarTheme: 'light' }) %>

  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-700 text-white p-8 sm:p-10 shadow-xl mb-8">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-300">Camverse Policies</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mt-2">Shipping Info</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-300 font-extralight">
          Details about shipping timelines, delivery coverage, and order tracking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Shipping Coverage</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            We deliver to most serviceable pin codes. Availability may vary based on product and location.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Dispatch Timeline</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Orders are usually processed quickly after confirmation. Dispatch time can vary during peak periods.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Delivery Timeline</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Delivery typically depends on destination and courier network. You will receive tracking details once shipped.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Order Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Track your order from your account orders section. Status updates are shown as your package moves.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Delivery Issues</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            If you face any delivery delay or issue, contact support from your order details page for assistance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/userFooter') %>
  <script src="/js/user/homePage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
